Inner Ice	Calm baseline vs environmental stress	Heart rate drop + cave darkness
Boundary Compression	Signal exceeding node boundary	CO₂ spike + EM turbulence
River Drift	Flow alignment	Environmental sensors + IMU movement
Storm Edge	Extreme state	Wind + EM + paradox flag


Harmonics Mapping:

