---

7. Security & Sovereignty

Local-first architecture: nodes retain raw signals; AI processes sanitized/mapped data

Plugin registration: whitelist-only, auto-audit, signatures checked

Data sovereignty: user owns logs, signals, derived patterns

Fallback protocols: offline operation, safe sync when possible



